    "Despite these challenges the results obtained exceed those of any laboratory setting experiment.",
    "With acknowledgement the advantages of in vivo studies, our in vitro study has some strengths too, such as mimicking the real process, and ability to obtain data within a shortened timeframe, which makes the study more manageable and easier to operationalize.",
